title: Chez Marche Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Macrobiotic, Organic, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Breakfast and lunch on Tue-Sat and dinner Wed-Fri. Try the fruit smoothies, peanut butter supreme, and Southwestern tofu wrap. Uses local and sustainable certified organic ingredients whenever possible. Live music, art shows, guest speakers, and small theater events.
